name: Protector
Lore: '''Chewie, this won''t help me. Hey! Save your strength. There''ll be another time. The princess...you have to take care of her.''',
Text: 'If Leia and Chewie are in a battle together, you may add two battle destiny. OR If Leia is participating in a battle, you may lose Chewie from hand to satisfy all battle damage and attrition against you. OR Cancel I''d Just As Soon Kiss A Wookiee or Frustration.',
